    "0": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "# 🎧 Service & Support — Customer Experience Quality Dashboard\n\n**Application:** [APP_NAME] (`APPLICATION-XXXXXXXXXXXX`) | **Data Source:** Gen 3 RUM (`user.events`, `user.sessions`)\n\n**[CLIENT_NAME] — Company — Company Objectives Tracked:**\n\n| Objective | KPIs on this Dashboard |\n|-----------|------------------------|\n| **Reduce Customer Complaints** | Sessions with errors, error-impacted session %, worst pages for user friction |\n| **Ensure Booking Completion** | Booking flow error rate, sessions failing to complete, SPA step failures |\n| **Improve Self-Service Experience** | Page responsiveness, session quality score, device/browser issue detection |\n| **Prioritise Support Resources** | Top error pages (where support tickets likely originate), known crash impact |\n| **Monitor Membership Experience** | Memberships page crash impact, affected visitor count |\n\n> **Usage:** Use this dashboard to understand the customer experience from a support perspective — which pages are causing frustration, how many sessions are error-impacted, and where the booking flow is breaking down. Helps correlate support tickets with real user data."
    },
